				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Mob hating me enough to cast a spell but not hit me??<a name="66521"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 12 04 1:16 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>This has been happening to me ALOT latley, im curious to see if it happens to other bards.
<br />

<br />
Let's say im in a WOS exp group, I'll pull a mob, Tank aggro's and we all start melee'ing. Sometimes the mob will, seemingly randomly, turn directly to face me, cast a snare (or whatever), then as soon as the casting animation is done turn back to face the tank. When this happens the mob dose'nt even attempt to melee me, and the HoTT target indicator does not so much as briefly flash my name.
<br />

<br />
I have no idea where this phantom aggro is coming from. Also whatever AI makes the mob turn, and cast a single spell on a low hate char, also makes no sense.
<br />

<br />
does this happen to anyone else? never seen it mentioned before.</span></td>
