				<td colspan="2"><span>It's what I wondered, that now we can see HoTT, then we see the mob's target more often, and the mobs hitting harder tend to be noticed more; the odd thing hitting for anything less than 100hp's doesn't get noticed these days.  
<br />
I can easily believe this always happened, but I just tend to notice it now.  Also noticed the debuffing cycle and it's true, I always end up with all the detrimental debuffs/dots that the mobs don't get chance to cast on anyone else in the party, so in the end, just get used to pulling buffless.  
<br />
Ta all for the shared info, all helps to understand what's happening.
